dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jason Clark. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Frances Henderson.
Nice to meet you, Frances. Could you please provide me with your policy number, which is a seven-digit number?
Sure, my policy number is eight seven four six two one five.
Thank you. And for security purposes, could you also confirm your date of birth for me?
Of course, my date of birth is the twenty-fifth of June, nineteen eighty-four.
Perfect, thank you for providing that information, Frances. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
Not at the moment, I just wanted to check on my claim status. Thank you.
You're welcome, Frances. Thank you for contacting us. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
